analysis.reasoning: Algorithm A places more clearly relevant shower cabins and typical shower fixtures at the top, with several strong product images showing installed cabins and visible discounts/badges that signal popular or good-value items. The top results in A feel more focused on the user intent 'Douches' (shower cabins and common shower components) and present higher-quality contextual images that aid selection. B contains similar items but surfaces a decorative/gold showerhead earlier and otherwise mixes small accessories among large cabin results more frequently, reducing immediate relevance and perceived value of the top slots.
